responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "241E43CF42E6DDA51EF7A9972EDCB0EB", "Traitors in the hills and no way to sort out the good arrivals from the bad ones. Keep your nose clean if you\'re passing through, but talk to Captain Avenmoor if you\'ve got any experience dealing with ruffians.")
